      "seed": 1958362068,
      "version": 148,
      "versionNonce": 250638548,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783843127532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "双指针：\nj 指向切片的开头\ni 指向切片的结尾",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "双指针：\nj 指向切片的开头\ni 指向切片的结尾",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "P7_ufKC5p-WxGDouoQW9r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -165.43194481531555,
      "y": -318.9745720756544,
      "width": 444.8198547363281,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2066456916,
      "version": 251,
      "versionNonce": 1797961324,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783843127532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "dp[i] 表示 s[0..i-1] 是否可以被字典中的单词拆分\n初始状态：dp[0] = true",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "dp[i] 表示 s[0..i-1] 是否可以被字典中的单词拆分\n初始状态：dp[0] = true",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Z6yOwi0Tgeu2NM9PnNXDi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 338.8004011846845,
      "y": -318.97457246289963,
      "width": 344.77996826171875,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4m",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1230264020,
      "version": 572,
      "versionNonce": 986920532,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783843127532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "遍历所有可能的切割点\n如果 dp[j] 可切并且切片在字典中存在\n那么 dp[i] 可切\n最终返回 dp[n] 即可",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "遍历所有可能的切割点\n如果 dp[j] 可切并且切片在字典中存在\n那么 dp[i] 可切\n最终返回 dp[n] 即可",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
